thread.title: Valued Customer

author: Valued Customer
title: Valued Customer
text:
request (70130)
Customer service was top notch. I bought some Haworth file cabinets off of Craigslist. They were missing the lock cores. The person at EasyKeys.com was able to identify which cores were compatible with a couple pictures I sent from my phone. They sent me a list of everything I needed with links. I also ordered a spare key for a different file cabinet which they had in stock. Free Fedex Shipping and a tutorial from YouTube had my file cabinets safe and secure.
